==Useful Info==
'''Broodmothers''' are enormous spiders found in the [[Spider's Nest]]. They have respectable combat stats, but also constantly summon smaller spiders in combat.

{{monster spells}}

==Tips & Tricks==
*Unlike most spiders, broodmothers are not weak to poison, though not resistant, either. Spells like [[Olgreb's Toxic Radiance]] can wear down the summons and the mother, but the broodmother's large HP pool makes taking them on directly with [[Alchemy]] less than ideal.

==History==
{{CBA|0.32|broodmothers won't be able to [[abjuration|abjure]] hostile summons.}}
*Broodmothers were added in [[0.28]].
